NICAM-DC
=========

The dynamical part of Non-hydrostatic ICosahedral Atmospheric Model.

Contributing
-----------
This code was developped by NICAM development team 
( JAMSTEC/RIGC , The University of Tokyo/AORI, RIKEN/AICS ).

